  <div class="content-section" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); margin-top: 0;">Global Fixes Applied (2026-04-19) — All 1308 Files</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--text-color);">
      The following global <code>sed</code> passes were run on ALL .tt files on 2026-04-19 (commit 255aefdf).
      Individual file audits still required to catch file-specific issues.
    </p>
    <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
      <li><strong>var(--light-color) → rgba(255,255,255,0.15)</strong> — eliminated undefined variable in 115 files</li>
      <li><strong>background: var(--secondary-color) → background: var(--nav-bg)</strong> — fixed summary/button elements</li>
      <li><strong>background-color: var(--secondary-color) → rgba(255,255,255,0.12)</strong> — fixed boxes and table rows</li>
      <li><strong>background-color: white/  #fff / #ffffff → rgba(255,255,255,0.88)</strong> — key application files</li>
      <li><strong>#f8f9fa → rgba(255,255,255,0.12)</strong> — FAQ and database_mode files</li>
      <li><strong>CSC combobox</strong> — converted to CSS variables</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

